s\\paperclip_fork_Enterprise\\ui\\src\\locales`\n\n**Agent Roles**\n\n**Developer** — localization developer: replaces hardcode with `t('key')`, maintains `en\\` and `ru\\` files, implements dropdown menu.\n\n**QA** — browser tester: checks server availability at [`http://127.0.0.1:3105/`](http://127.0.0.1:3105/), searches for unreplaced English strings when Russian language is active, updates MAP file.\n\n**Orchestrator** — monitors the last update date of MAP file; if file is updated — starts new Developer → QA cycle.\n\n**Statuses in MAP File**\n\n| Status         | Set By        | Meaning                                          |\n| -------------- | ------------- | ------------------------------------------------ |\n| TODO           | Browser agent | Found English text, needs localization           |\n| DONE           | Developer     | Localization completed, awaiting QA verification |\n| TODO + comment | QA            | Checked, found problem, returned to Developer    |\n| QA\\_OK         | QA            | Checked, everything works correctly              |\n\n**Working Cycle (Loop)**\n\n```\nBrowser agent → TODO\n      ↓\nDeveloper → DONE\n      ↓\nQA checks DONE\n      ↓\n  [not OK] → TODO + comment → Developer → DONE → QA...\n  [OK]    → QA_OK\n\n```\n\n**Plan**\n\n**Step 1 — Browser agent: audit of visible English elements**\n\n* Opens [http://127.0.0.1:3105/](http://127.0.0.1:3105/), switches to Russian language.\n* Goes through all available screens.\n* For each found English text, records in MAP file:\n  * full element text\n  * HTML element\n  * CSS selector\n  * status TODO\n\n**Step 2 — Developer: hardcode replacement**\n\n* Takes records with TODO status from MAP file.\n* By text, HTML element and CSS selector finds location in codebase.\n* Replaces with t('key'), adds translations to en\\ and ru.\n* Sets status DONE.\n\n**Step 3 — QA: DONE verification**\n\n* Receives signal about appearance of records with DONE status in MAP file.\n* First basic check: [http://127.0.0.1:3105/](http://127.0.0.1:3105/) responds and not black screen. If black screen — cycle stops, Developer fixes.\n* Switches to Russian language, checks specific elements from DONE records.\n* If problem — changes status back to TODO with comment on what exactly is wrong.\n* If everything is correct — sets QA\\_OK.\n\n**Step 4 — Iteration**\n\n* Browser agent again goes through all screens searching for remaining English strings.\n* New strings → TODO, cycle repeats.\n* Orchestrator starts new cycle with each appearance of TODO in MAP file.\n\n**Final Verification (when all records are QA\\_OK)**\n\n* QA goes through all records with QA\\_OK status — full regression run.\n* Checks that previously completed localization hasn't broken during subsequent changes.\n* If something broke — record returns to TODO with comment, cycle resumes.\n* If everything is fine — project is considered completed.\n\n**Completion Criterion**\n\nAll records in MAP file have QA\\_OK status, final regression run is passed, server [http://127.0.0.1:3105/](http://127.0.0.1:3105/) loads stably.","status":"planned","leadAgentId":null,"targetDate":null,"color":"#14b8a6","env":null,"pauseReason":null,"pausedAt":null,"executionWorkspacePolicy":null,"archivedAt":null,"createdAt":"2026-05-04T07:09:48.516Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-06T19:29:42.813Z","urlKey":"localization","goalIds":[],"goals":[],"codebase":{"workspaceId":"047a7078-fce3-46a4-aa5e-d66abc0a3f51","repoUrl":"https://github.com/AngelCard-CC-Non-Cancellation-Guarantee/paperclip_fork_Enterprise.git","repoRef":null,"defaultRef":null,"repoName":"paperclip_fork_Enterprise","localFolder":"C:\\Users\\vibecoder_blogger\\PycharmProjects\\paperclip_fork_Enterprise","managedFolder":"C:\\Users\\vibecoder_blogger\\.paperclip\\instances\\default\\projects\\13e61789-5895-451b-95a8-a7457a310c9e\\90d1b267-8b11-4b20-abed-2422cd4089fb\\paperclip_fork_Enterprise","effectiveLocalFolder":"C:\\Users\\vibecoder_blogger\\PycharmProjects\\paperclip